(176, 1, '2016-01-29 06:04:22', '2016-01-29 06:04:22', '[:en]<img src="http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/about3-300x162.jpg" alt="about3" width="300" height="162" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-60" />\r\n<br>\r\nAt vero eos et accusamus et iusto odio dignissimos ducimus qui blanditiis praesentium voluptatum deleniti atque corrupti quos dolores et quas molestias excepturi sint occaecati cupiditate non provident, similique sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollitia animi, id est laborum et dolorum fuga. Et harum quidem rerum facilis est et expedita distinctio. Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi optio cumque nihil impedit quo minus id quod maxime placeat facere possimus, omnis voluptas assumenda est, omnis dolor repellendus. Temporibus autem quibusdam et aut officiis debitis aut rerum necessitatibus saepe eveniet ut et voluptates repudiandae sint et molestiae non recusandae. Itaque earum rerum hic tenetur a sapiente delectus, ut aut reiciendis voluptatibus maiores alias consequatur aut perferendis doloribus asperiores repellat[:ja]<img src="http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/about3-300x162.jpg" alt="about3" width="300" height="162" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-60" />\r\n<br>\r\n日本国内屈指の生物多様性を誇る沖縄県。\r\n　その沖縄本島内に24の調査地点（森林12、開放地12：14サイトは島内で既に稼働中）を設け、継続的に飛翔性昆虫や地上徘徊性昆虫、気象データなどを収集。採集された標本群と、最新の遺伝子解析技術の組み合わせにより、沖縄県の生物多様性を使った、世界最先端の生物多様性研究を行なうプロジェクト。\r\n　さらに、昆虫以外の調査データを含めた全データの積極的な公開システムを構築。データの共同利用と研究ネットワーク構築を推進し、沖縄発信で世界の生物多様性研究に貢献することを目指す。\r\n[:]', '[:en]The beginning of the OKEON project: What is it?[:ja]Current Status[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 06:04:22', '2016-01-29 06:04:22', '', 87, 'http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/?p=176', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(177, 1, '2016-01-29 06:06:36', '2016-01-29 06:06:36', '[:en]<img src="http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/about3-300x162.jpg" alt="about3" width="300" height="162" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-60" />\r\n<br>\r\nAt vero eos et accusamus et iusto odio dignissimos ducimus qui blanditiis praesentium voluptatum deleniti atque corrupti quos dolores et quas molestias excepturi sint occaecati cupiditate non provident, similique sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollitia animi, id est laborum et dolorum fuga. Et harum quidem rerum facilis est et expedita distinctio. Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi optio cumque nihil impedit quo minus id quod maxime placeat facere possimus, omnis voluptas assumenda est, omnis dolor repellendus. Temporibus autem quibusdam et aut officiis debitis aut rerum necessitatibus saepe eveniet ut et voluptates repudiandae sint et molestiae non recusandae. Itaque earum rerum hic tenetur a sapiente delectus, ut aut reiciendis voluptatibus maiores alias consequatur aut perferendis doloribus asperiores repellat[:ja]<img src="http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/about3-300x162.jpg" alt="about3" width="300" height="162" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-60" />\r\n<br>\r\n日本国内屈指の生物多様性を誇る沖縄県。\r\n　その沖縄本島内に24の調査地点（森林12、開放地12：14サイトは島内で既に稼働中）を設け、継続的に飛翔性昆虫や地上徘徊性昆虫、気象データなどを収集。採集された標本群と、最新の遺伝子解析技術の組み合わせにより、沖縄県の生物多様性を使った、世界最先端の生物多様性研究を行なうプロジェクト。\r\n　さらに、昆虫以外の調査データを含めた全データの積極的な公開システムを構築。データの共同利用と研究ネットワーク構築を推進し、沖縄発信で世界の生物多様性研究に貢献することを目指す。\r\n[:]', '[:en]The beginning of the OKEON project: What is it?[:ja]OKEONとは？[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 06:06:36', '2016-01-29 06:06:36', '', 87, 'http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/?p=177', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(178, 1, '2016-01-29 06:07:59', '2016-01-29 06:07:59', '[:en]<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-63" src="http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/about6-300x162.jpg" alt="about6" width="300" height="162" />\r\n\r\nEt harum quidem rerum facilis est et expedita distinctio. Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi optio cumque nihil impedit quo minus id quod maxime placeat facere possimus, omnis voluptas assumenda est, omnis dolor repellendus. Temporibus autem quibusdam et aut officiis debitis aut rerum necessitatibus saepe eveniet ut et voluptates repudiandae sint et molestiae non recusandae.[:ja]<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-63" src="http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/about6-300x162.jpg" alt="about6" width="300" height="162" />\r\n\r\n日本語のロラムイップサム[:]', '[:en]Setting up sites across Okinawa[:ja]ポスト二番目[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '96-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 06:07:59', '2016-01-29 06:07:59', '', 96, 'http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/?p=178', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(179, 1, '2016-01-29 06:11:14', '2016-01-29 06:11:14', '[:en]The biodiversity and biocomplexity unit participated in OIST’s November 8th 2015 Open Campus and set up a booth to exhibit the “Wonders of Ants”.\r\nDisplays ranged from live ant specimens to pinned ant specimen that could be viewed under a microscope to stereographic ant images that becomes 3D with proper glasses. A novel aspect in this year’s event include a slam trap display, which is meant to demonstrate to the public a method we use to collect ants which is also the main method being used to collect insects for the OKEON project. Two 3D printed ants along with the original specimens from which they were made were also exhibited. \r\n[:ja]おはようございます！[:]', '[:en]OKEON Open Campus[:ja]OKEON オープンキャンパス[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '131-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 06:11:14', '2016-01-29 06:11:14', '', 131, 'http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/?p=179', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(180, 1, '2016-01-29 06:12:38', '2016-01-29 06:12:38', '[:en]Mr. Hidetsune Takamine is a well-known Okinawan ant expert who has been collecting ants in Okinawa for around 40 years. His collection includes 116 species, 30 of which are endemic to Okinawa.\r\n\r\nOn November 26, 2015, Mr. Takamine donated his ant collection to OIST at a handover ceremony that took place at the Biodiversity and Biocomplexity Unit and will be stored in the unit’s specimen shelf as the Takamine Collection.\r\n\r\nDr. Masashi Yoshimura and Prof. Evan Economo expressed their gratitude towards Mr. Takamine, emphasizing how much this donation would contribute to academic research and more specifically how it would improve the scientific research on Okinawan biodiversity and help us understand how the diversity of Okinawa fits into the broader picture.[:ja]ウミガメを見ました[:]', '[:en]Takamine Ant Collection[:ja]高峰さんの蟻[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 06:12:38', '2016-01-29 06:12:38', '', 133, 'http://localhost:8888/localwp.com/?p=180', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
